      "amount": "to taste"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Grate the daikon and set aside.",
    "In a shallow dish, whisk together tahini, rice vinegar, and maple syrup.",
    "Heat coconut oil in a deep frying pan to 325°F (165°C).",
    "Dredge the daikon in the tahini mixture, then carefully place in the hot oil.",
    "Fry for 3-4 minutes, or until the daikon is golden brown and crispy.",
    "Drain the daikon on paper towels and sprinkle with sesame seeds.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately.",
    "Season with crushed black pepper to taste."
